snippet.title: ひぐらしデイブレイクPortable (Higurashi Daybreak Portable) Trailer
snippet.description:
[Release Date (JPN) : 27th November 2008]

Remember back in my Higurashi Daybreak Netplay video where I mentioned the PSP version being in development?

This is the trailer and nothing much has changed, except the art style and animation. Enjoy!
